headline: Expedia price target raised to $180 from $150 at Morgan Stanley
summary: Morgan Stanley raised the firm’s price target on Expedia (EXPE) to $180 from $150 and keeps an Equal Weight rating on the shares. Expedia is executing better and the firm now models 8% room night growth in FY25 while raising its FY25 and FY26 Bookings forecasts by 6% and 8% and EBITDA views by 5% and 7%, respectively.
